      <title>法国互联网电缆在奥运会期间遭遇最新攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/french-internet-cables-severed-in-latest-attack-during-olympics</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在奥运会期间，法国基础设施遭遇的最新一次袭击导致法国南部和东部地区传输宽带服务的多条光缆一夜之间被切断。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/french-internet-cables-severed-in-latest-attack-during-olympics</guid>
