      <title>阿里巴巴计划提高商家服务费 股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/alibaba-shares-jump-on-plans-to-boost-service-fee-for-merchants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿里巴巴集团控股有限公司股价创下两个月来最大涨幅，因投资者对这家电子商务公司从商家赚取更多服务费的计划表示欢迎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/alibaba-shares-jump-on-plans-to-boost-service-fee-for-merchants</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 06:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国铺设天堂之路并修建停车场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-29/paved-over-gardens-are-environmental-warfare</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在一个以美丽的风景而闻名的国家，房主对混凝土的吸引力超过了对绿化的吸引力，这导致了意想不到的环境后果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-07-29/paved-over-gardens-are-environmental-warfare</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 04:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国电网巨头计划投入创纪录资金缓解电力瓶颈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-grid-giant-plans-record-spending-to-ease-power-bottlenecks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国主要电网运营商将把支出提高到创纪录的水平，以缓解输电瓶颈，凸显出北京方面推动可再生能源使用的举措，并可能使铜等金属受益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/china-grid-giant-plans-record-spending-to-ease-power-bottlenecks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 03:45:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小米斥资 1.16 亿美元购入北京工厂，扩大电动汽车生产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/xiaomi-buys-116-million-site-in-beijing-to-expand-ev-production</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继首款轿车取得成功后，中国科技公司小米集团斥资 8.42 亿元人民币（1.16 亿美元）在北京购买了一块土地，用于扩大电动汽车产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/xiaomi-buys-116-million-site-in-beijing-to-expand-ev-production</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 03:45:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
